### 5.5 API Requirements

**REST API Endpoints:**

```
# Projects
POST   /api/projects              # Create project
GET    /api/projects              # List user projects
GET    /api/projects/:id          # Get project details
PUT    /api/projects/:id          # Update project
DELETE /api/projects/:id          # Delete project

# Components
POST   /api/projects/:id/components     # Add component
PUT    /api/projects/:id/components/:cid # Update component
DELETE /api/projects/:id/components/:cid # Remove component

# Modules
GET    /api/modules               # List available modules
GET    /api/modules/:id           # Get module details
POST   /api/projects/:id/modules  # Install module
DELETE /api/projects/:id/modules/:mid # Uninstall module

# Functions
GET    /api/functions             # List available functions
GET    /api/functions/:id         # Get function details
POST   /api/functions/execute     # Execute function (testing)

# Code Generation
POST   /api/generate/web          # Generate Next.js code
POST   /api/generate/mobile       # Generate React Native code
POST   /api/generate/api          # Generate API code
POST   /api/generate/database     # Generate database schema

# Deployment
POST   /api/deploy/web            # Deploy web app
POST   /api/deploy/mobile         # Deploy mobile app
POST   /api/deploy/ota            # Push OTA update
GET    /api/deploy/status/:id     # Check deployment status

# Version Control
POST   /api/git/commit            # Commit changes
POST   /api/git/push              # Push to remote
GET    /api/git/history           # Get commit history
POST   /api/git/rollback          # Rollback to commit

# User Management
GET    /api/user/profile          # Get user profile
PUT    /api/user/profile          # Update profile
GET    /api/user/projects         # List user projects
```

**API Response Format:**

```typescript
interface APIResponse<T> {
  success: boolean;
  data?: T;
  error?: {
    code: string;
    message: string;
    details?: any;
  };
  metadata?: {
    timestamp: string;
    requestId: string;
    version: string;
  };
}

// Success example
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "proj_123",
    "name": "My App",
    "createdAt": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
  },
  "metadata": {
    "timestamp": "2025-01-01T00:00:01Z",
    "requestId": "req_456",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  }
}

// Error example
{
  "success": false,
  "error": {
    "code": "PROJECT_NOT_FOUND",
    "message": "Project with ID 'proj_123' not found",
    "details": {
      "projectId": "proj_123"
    }
  },
  "metadata": {
    "timestamp": "2025-01-01T00:00:01Z",
    "requestId": "req_456",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  }
}
```

**Rate Limits:**
- Anonymous: 10 requests/minute
- Authenticated: 100 requests/minute
- Premium: 1000 requests/minute
- Deployment: 10 per hour

