- Snap to grid (toggleable)
- Rulers showing pixel measurements
- Guidelines when aligning components
- Multi-select (Shift + Click or drag rectangle)
- Copy/paste (Ctrl+C / Ctrl+V)
- Undo/redo (Ctrl+Z / Ctrl+Y) - 100 history states
- Component hover highlights
- Selection box with resize handles
- Right-click context menu

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- Canvas loads in < 2 seconds
- 60 FPS performance with 100+ components
- Smooth zooming and panning
- Accurate pixel-perfect positioning
- No layout shifts during interaction

