**Requirements:**
- Searchable component list
- Categories: Basic, Layout, Forms, Media, Social, Commerce, etc.
- Favorites system (star components)
- Recently used section
- Preview thumbnail for each component
- Drag to canvas or click to add
- Tooltip with component description
- Filter by module (show only installed modules)

**Component Categories:**

**Basic:**
- Text, Heading, Paragraph
