- Image, Image Gallery
- Video Player
- Audio Player
- Carousel
- Lightbox

**Navigation:**
- Header, Footer
- Navigation Menu
- Breadcrumbs
- Pagination
- Sidebar

**Data Display:**
- Table
- List (ordered, unordered)
- Data Grid
- Chart (line, bar, pie)
- Progress Bar
- Badge, Tag
- Avatar
- Stat Card

**Feedback:**
- Alert, Toast
- Modal, Dialog
- Tooltip, Popover
- Loading Spinner
- Skeleton Loader
- Empty State

