## 16. Infrastructure & DevOps

### 16.1 CI/CD Pipeline

**GitHub Actions Workflow:**

```yaml
name: CI/CD

on:
  push:
    branches: [main, develop]
  pull_request:
    branches: [main, develop]

jobs:
  test:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
      
      - name: Setup Node.js
        uses: actions/setup-node@v3
        with:
          node-version: '18'
          cache: 'npm'
      
      - name: Install dependencies
        run: npm ci
      
      - name: Lint
        run: npm run lint
      
      - name: Type check
        run: npm run type-check
      
      - name: Unit tests
        run: npm run test
      
      - name: E2E tests
        run: npm run test:e2e
      
      - name: Upload coverage
        uses: codecov/codecov-action@v3

  build:
    needs: test
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
      
      - name: Setup Node.js
        uses: actions/setup-node@v3
        with:
          node-version: '18'
          cache: 'npm'
      
      - name: Install dependencies
        run: npm ci
      
      - name: Build
        run: npm run build
      
      - name: Upload build artifacts
        uses: actions/upload-artifact@v3
        with:
          name: build
          path: .next

  deploy:
    needs: build
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    if: github.ref == 'refs/heads/main'
    steps:
      - name: Deploy to Vercel
        uses: amondnet/vercel-action@v25
        with:
          vercel-token: ${{ secrets.VERCEL_TOKEN }}
          vercel-org-id: ${{ secrets.VERCEL_ORG_ID }}
          vercel-project-id: ${{ secrets.VERCEL_PROJECT_ID }}
          vercel-args: '--prod'
```

### 16.2 Environments

**Development:**
- URL: http://localhost:3000
- Database: Local Supabase
- Purpose: Local development

**Staging:**
- URL: https://staging.devbasestudio.com
- Database: Staging Supabase
- Purpose: Testing before production

**Production:**
- URL: https://devbasestudio.com
- Database: Production Supabase
- Purpose: Live application

### 16.3 Monitoring

**Tools:**
- Vercel Analytics (web performance)
- Sentry (error tracking)
- PostHog (product analytics)
- Supabase Dashboard (database metrics)

**Metrics to Track:**
- Error rate
- Response time (P50, P95, P99)
- Uptime (target: 99.9%)
- Database query performance
- Deployment frequency
- Mean Time to Recovery (MTTR)

**Alerts:**
- Error rate > 1%
- Response time P95 > 1s
- Uptime < 99.9%
- Database CPU > 80%
- Deployment failed

### 16.4 Backup & Recovery

**Database Backups:**
- Automated daily backups (Supabase)
- Point-in-time recovery (7 days)
- Manual backup before major changes
- Backup retention: 90 days
- Test restore monthly

**Code Backups:**
- Git version control
- GitHub as primary remote
- GitLab as backup remote
- Code signed commits

**Recovery Time Objectives:**
- RTO (Recovery Time): < 4 hours
- RPO (Recovery Point): < 24 hours

