## 25. Appendices

### Appendix A: Glossary

- **AST**: Abstract Syntax Tree - A tree representation of code structure
- **CDN**: Content Delivery Network - Distributed servers for fast content delivery
- **EAS**: Expo Application Services - Cloud build service for React Native
- **GPL**: GNU General Public License - Open source license
- **JWT**: JSON Web Token - Token-based authentication
- **OTA**: Over-The-Air - Remote app updates without app store
- **RLS**: Row Level Security - Database-level access control
- **SDK**: Software Development Kit - Set of tools for development
- **SSO**: Single Sign-On - One login for multiple services
- **UI Kit**: Design system with pre-built components
- **WCAG**: Web Content Accessibility Guidelines

### Appendix B: References

**Technical Documentation:**
- React: https://react.dev
- Next.js: https://nextjs.org
- React Native: https://reactnative.dev
- Expo: https://docs.expo.dev
- Supabase: https://supabase.com/docs
- Tailwind CSS: https://tailwindcss.com
- shadcn/ui: https://ui.shadcn.com

**Standards:**
- WCAG 2.1: https://www.w3.org/WAI/WCAG21/quickref/
- OAuth 2.0: https://oauth.net/2/
- OpenAPI: https://swagger.io/specification/
- Semantic Versioning: https://semver.org

**Inspiration:**
